Description: A Non-Linear Video Editing Suite for KDE
 Kdenlive! (pronounced Kay-den-live) is a Non-Linear Video Editing Suite for
 KDE environment running on Linux.
 .
 It is based on the MLT video framework which relies on the FFMPEG project.

